text.__SUMMARY__:
Pultenaea sp. Genowlan Point is a critically endangered undescribed species of flowering plant in the family Fabaceae–Faboideae. It is only known from one population at Genowlan Point (33.08535°S 150.07341°E﻿ / -33.08535; 150.07341) in the Capertee Valley within the Rylstone local government area of New South Wales.
